Description: render rich text and progress bars in the terminal (Avalan PPA pin)
 rich is a Python library for writing rich text — colour, styles,
 tables, progress bars, markdown, syntax highlighting and more — to
 the terminal. This rebuild pins 14.3.4 because Debian sid carries
 15.x, which is above the upper bound Avalan tracks (>= 14.1, < 15).
